  <brief_title>Cognitive-behavioural Treatment of Chronic Back Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study to Compare a Cognitive-behavioral Treatment With a Cognitive-behavioral Treatment With Biofeedback Elements to Patients With Chronic (Low) Back Pain</official_title>
  <sponsors>
